container.value: RM18D, 27/F, Ho King Comm CTR, 2-16 Fayuen ST, Mongkok Kowloon, Hong Kong

creator: Yunbu Game Studio
descriptionHtml:
The gorgeous match 3 puzzle game with magic boosters and sweet candies! Start the happy and mystery journey with various candies in sweet wonderland,the Candy Island!We have thousands of match 3 games and candy puzzle games to enjoy! Each candy puzzle comes jam-packed with candy matching fun and jelly matching thrills!

Solve puzzles with quick thinking and smart moves!Design your moves by matching 3 or more candies in a row, use boosters wisely to overcome those extra sticky puzzles!

Features:
🍭- Lollipop: Sweet lollipop help you to smash the any candy you want to crush.
🍭- Bust rocket: Help you to crush a vertical column of sweet candy.
🍭- Magic wand: Magic wand allows you to re-arrange the candy interface.
🍭- Magic gloves: This glove from the hands of magician, you can let you exchange any two candies.
🍭- Spacecraft: This skill can help you collect all the same candies at once.


Notes:
✨WIFI FREE! TIME FREE!
✨ There are many free tasty rewards,guaranteed to have you wanting more.
✨Deliciously sweet supply of candy smashing power-ups and combos.
✨ Easy and funny to play, yet challenging to fully master.
✨ From easy to hard for all people to enjoy – available on-the-go, offline and online.It's easy to sync the game between devices and unlock full game features when connected to the Internet or Wifi.
✨Thousands of the best levels and puzzles in the Candy Island, more on the way.
✨ Facebook sync, you can login your Facebook account and play with your friends!
✨Get to the top of the friends leaderboard and compare scores with your friends!
